{"id":944843,"date":[{"year":1994,"month":5,"day":30}],"page":"7","source":"《北京青年报》","region":"","masthead":"中外文摘","special_issue":"中外文摘","column":"","genre":"","count":"116","ytitle":"","mtitle":"健康的定义","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界卫生组织对健康的定义是:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1.精力充沛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2.乐观处事；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3.睡眠良好；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4.适应能力强；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"5.能抵抗一般性疾病；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"6.保持标准体重；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"7.眼睛明亮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"8.牙齿完整；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"9.头发有光泽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"10.肌肉皮肤弹性好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(原载《北京青年报》)"}]}